protected)\n- `CRUD /user/urls/{id}` (protected)\n- `GET /auth/login/{provider}` — public OIDC initiation\n- `GET /auth/callback` — public OIDC callback\n- `POST /auth/logout` — protected\n- `POST /auth/register` — new user username registration\n\n**Database (PostgreSQL):** Tables: `Users`, `UserProviders`, `ShortenedUrls`, `UrlClicks`, `UserQuotas`, `UserAnomalies`\n\n**Frontend (Vue.js):**\n- UI library: `shadcn/vue` + Tailwind CSS\n- Type-safe API client: `openapi-typescript-codegen` (generate from OpenAPI spec)\n- State management: Pinia\n- Testing: Vitest + `@vue/test-utils`, 80% coverage minimum\n- Build tool implied: Vite\n\n**Logging:** Go `slog` (stdlib), JSON to stdout. Lightweight in-memory Prometheus-style metrics at `/api/metrics`.\n\n**Resource targets:** <10 MB logging overhead, tuned Gin/GORM/Postgres for 4 GB RAM.\n\n---\n\n## 4. Frontend Config Files\n\n**None exist.** The `frontend/` directory is completely empty — no `package.json`, `vite.config.*`, `tsconfig.*`, or any other file.\n\n---\n\n## 5. Backend Tech Stack Summary\n\nThe `backend/` directory has the scaffolded folder structure but **all subdirectories are empty** — no source files exist yet:\n\n| Path | Status |\n|---|---|\n| `backend/business-logic/models/` | Empty |\n| `backend/handlers/` | Empty |\n| `backend/infrastructure/pg/` | Empty |\n\nNo `go.mod`, `go.sum`, `Dockerfile`, or `docker-compose` files exist anywhere in the workspace.\n\n**Planned stack:** Go + Gin + GORM + PostgreSQL + golang-migrate + swag/gin-swagger + go-oidc + golang-jwt.\n\n---\n\n**Summary:** This project is in the very early scaffolding phase. Only the directory skeleton and planning documents exist — no code has been written yet in either the frontend or backend.","tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01117qVqeTksq7ifo3odpHWP__vscode-1772533729893","cwd":"/Volumes/transcend/src/pet/linkshortener"}

